:{{DIcon|Talk}} What trouble have you gotten yourself into this time?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504108103-->
::'''Piso:''' This one really wasn't my fault! As my dad's birthday's coming up, I thought I'd make him some gloves outta leather, so I've been out in the woods a lot lately.
::'''Piso:''' But... but I skipped a few classes to do it, and now Miss Pythias is on my tail...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504108002_37-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504108002_37-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Couldn't you just explain everything to your dad?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504108106-->
:::'''Piso:''' No way! That'd spoil the fun! If I can't get him shocked and impressed at the same time, all this effort will go to waste!
:::'''Piso:''' And besides... does he look like someone who listens to explanations? Every time it's the same thing &mdash; no questions, just the cane!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504108119-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504108119-->
:::'''Piso:''' Anyway, don't worry, Mr. Phainon. I'm your number one follower. Even if you leave to explore the world, I'll keep all the brats here in line.
:::'''Piso:''' And when you two become legendary heroes, Livia and I will come join you. You've gotta tell us all about your adventures and feed us tons of delicious stuff!
:::'''Piso:''' It's a deal. Don't you dare forget!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} A few classes, huh?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504108109-->
:::'''Piso:''' D&mdash;Don't sweat the details! It's not like I skipped class just to goof off this time...
:::'''Piso:''' But promise me, Mr. Phainon, you won't rat me out, okay? Or my behind's really gonna be toast.
:::'''Piso:''' If my dad asks, just say I'm by the granary. That's where I usually hide anyway.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504108119-->
